No. D-2467. In the Matter of Discipline of Montgomery Blair Sibley. 559 U.S. 1002, 130 S. Ct. 1947,

176 L. Ed. 2d 411,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 2535. March 22, 2010.

Montgomery Blair Sib-ley, of Washington, District of Columbia, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
